  "title": "JANITOR SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Work closely with the Manager to ensure smooth operations.</li>\n  <li>Supervise &amp; assist a team of crew on site.</li>\n  <li>Maintain &amp; control the use of stock, equipment &amp; consumables.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Manager in maintaining up-to-date asset list.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Manager in scheduling for jobs &amp; holiday leaves.</li>\n  <li>Monitor performance &amp; absenteeism of crew.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that appropriate PPE are worn by crew.</li>\n  <li>Prepare overtime rosters for approval by the Manager.</li>\n  <li>Upkeep all equipment.</li>\n  <li>Ensure company policies &amp; standards are met by crew at all faclities.</li>\n  <li>Liaise &amp; monitor work done by outsourced contractors.</li>\n  <li>Other duties assigned by the Manager or the Managerment.</li>\n</ul>",
